  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: You say the mine shaft was broken open from the inside?
    nextOption: That's what it looked like
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: And there was a glowing coming from the mine shaft?
    nextOption: Yes
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'The graveyard was built on top of an old mine.


      Crystals
      like the one you found on the skeleton used to be mined there.


      However,
      the mine entrance was sealed up long ago when crystals ran out.'
    nextOption: Was something sealed inside?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'The mine was completely empty.


      The crystals never glowed
      like this either.'
    nextOption: Strange...
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: Go investigate the mine.
    nextOption: All Alone?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'It would take a terrifyingly strong creature to break the seal
      open from the inside.


      See if you can find out what it was.'
    nextOption: Are you sure you don't want to come help?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'I''ll be here in the hiding in the safety of...


      I mean...
      um... taking care of some important business in my tent.


      Now get to
      it recruit!'
    nextOption: Yes Sir
  prerequisiteConditions: []
